short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Open current position on an other map with one click.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Supported maps are: Google Maps, Komoot, SwissTopo, Openstreetmap and Bikerouter.

Were you ever planning an adventure, zoomed in into an area and wanted to see if other maps show more helpful information, but finding this exact spot is hard? Map Position Transfer is the solution! Quickly switch between maps with a single click.
